room_title: Escape room "Missing Miss Marie" by Speakeasy Escape Room in Virginia Beach
room_description: Was she murdered?  Was she taken?  Did she quit?  The Music Box Theater's leading lady has gone missing.  See if you can get the scoop and convince her to come work for the club. We know the fuzz is after her too so time is of the essence. We'll sneak ya out of the Tiger and into the backstage, but get out quick, we can only stall the cops for so long!
